By "bonehead" he means the file with the skull as its icon (  TOBW.rtfd)  It says "Use any fake email and fake serial to register with!"

The Bonehead file refers to an icon in the .DMG file. If you click it, it opens a text document that basically tells you to just register with any email and any made up registration number - do that and everything works fine.
